<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Accès refusé — SchoolPrepar</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap/5.3.3/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 50%, #0f3460 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        }
        .error-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
            max-width: 480px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }
        .lock-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: block;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
            50% { transform: scale(1.08); opacity: 0.85; }
        }
        .error-code {
            font-size: 5rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb, #f5576c);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            line-height: 1;
        }
        .error-title { font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 1rem 0 .5rem; }
        .error-msg { color: rgba(255,255,255,.65); font-size: .95rem; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        .btn-home {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            padding: .75rem 2rem;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: all .2s;
        }
        .btn-home:hover { opacity: .9; transform: translateY(-2px); color: #fff; }
        .btn-back {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);
            border-radius: 50px;
            padding: .75rem 2rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,.8);
            font-weight: 500;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-left: .75rem;
            transition: all .2s;
        }
        .btn-back:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,.2); color: #fff; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="error-card">
    <span class="lock-icon">🔐</span>
    <div class="error-code">403</div>
    <h1 class="error-title">Accès refusé</h1>
    <p class="error-msg">
        Vous n'êtes pas autorisé à accéder à cette interface.<br>
        Cette zone est réservée aux administrateurs de la plateforme SchoolPrepar.
    </p>
    <div>
        <a href="/" class="btn-home"><i class="fas fa-home me-2"></i>Retour à l'accueil</a>
        <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="btn-back"><i class="fas fa-arrow-left me-1"></i>Retour</a>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
